          <h3 id="habitat-loss">Habitat Loss: Destroying the Stopovers</h3>

          <div class="section-header-with-audio">
            <h4>The Yellow Sea Bottleneck</h4>
            <button class="audio-btn" id="habitat-loss-audio" title="Listen to Dr Eliot explain this">&#9654;</button>
